<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='502159' id='t-502159'>Ads for Coca-Cola and beer always depict</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='505423' id='t-505423'>smiling young people,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='506978' id='t-506978'>even though old as well as young people</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='508948' id='t-508948'>buy and drink Coca-Cola and beer.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='511270' id='t-511270'>Just think, what's the last time you saw</span>
