<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='530609' id='t-530609'>compared to their status in traditional societies?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='533998' id='t-533998'>There have been a few changes for the better</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='535868' id='t-535868'>and more changes for the worse.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='538073' id='t-538073'>Big changes for the better</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='539674' id='t-539674'>include the fact that today we enjoy</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='541825' id='t-541825'>much longer lives,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='543809' id='t-543809'>much better health in our old age,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='546103' id='t-546103'>and much better recreational opportunities.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='549741' id='t-549741'>Another change for the better is that we now have</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='552011' id='t-552011'>specialized retirement facilities</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='554851' id='t-554851'>and programs to take care of old people.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='558202' id='t-558202'>Changes for the worse begin with the cruel reality</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='561070' id='t-561070'>that we now have</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='562759' id='t-562759'>more old people and fewer young people</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='565333' id='t-565333'>than at any time in the past.</span>
