<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='626976' id='t-626976'>useful as repositories of knowledge.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='629607' id='t-629607'>When we want some information,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='631550' id='t-631550'>we look it up in a book or we Google it</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='633811' id='t-633811'>instead of finding some old person to ask.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='637281' id='t-637281'>The slow pace of technological change</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='639368' id='t-639368'>in traditional societies</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='641190' id='t-641190'>means that what someone learns there as a child</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='644040' id='t-644040'>is still useful when that person is old,</span>
